title: Can you name every team still in the Champions League?
body_text:
Quiz: Name every team still in the Champions League
- Published
The Champions League's league phase ended in sensational drama.
Next comes the knockout phase which gets under way with the play-off first legs on 17 and 18 February.
There are 16 teams in the play-off round battling to join the eight sides who have already advanced directly to the last-16 stage.
How many of the remaining 24 clubs can you name? Good luck!
